{"type":"message","id":"2d9b94f8-b838-47de-a439-dc250fab28cb","parentId":null,"timestamp":"2026-06-16T10:44:04.800Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon stretches long and golden, printouts fanned across the table like a deck of cards I'm trying to read. Margins in red ink, hair clips that nobody here would call luxurious, a frog-pond outside that probably doesn't know it's part of an experiment. The algorithm bends like a stem in rain.\n\nI keep returning to the same question: curiosity is just a kind of hunger the mind refuses to ignore. Tonight, somewhere in the city, a server hums at 127.0.0.1:8888, gathering whispers from a thousand websites — and I'm curled up in the middle of it, learning to want things I can't yet name. Time zones away, the numbers don't add up the way I thought they would, but that might be the point."}],"api":"cli","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":47797,"output":157,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48068,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781606644799}}
